data.description: This stunning home in Deltona is waiting just for you! With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms sprawling across 1,564 sq ft of meticulously curated living space, this home has something everyone in the family will love. Having undergone significant upgrades just last year, including the installation of a new roof, AC system, water heater, and a water softener system, along with stylishly revamped bathrooms and refreshed flooring in the living areas, you can have peace of mind knowing this property has been cared for. Additionally, the recently replaced windows not only elevate the home's aesthetic appeal but also enhance energy efficiency. Step inside to discover an open layout that seamlessly merges formal dining and living spaces, accentuated by charming brick walls enveloping the kitchen area, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen stands as the heart of this home, boasting not only ample storage and counter space but also a breakfast bar that overlooks the welcoming family room. With direct access to the screened-in patio, the family room offers a seamless transition to the outdoors, inviting you to relax and unwind in this serene setting. Stepping outside, you're greeted by an expansive fenced backyard, providing an ideal space for four legged friends or little ones to play freely. Situated in a peaceful locale yet conveniently close to major highways, shopping centers, delectable dining options, nature preserves, natural springs, and scenic hiking trails, this residence ensures a serene haven while remaining less than 40 minutes from the allure of picturesque beaches and the vibrant bustle of downtown Orlando. Additionally, it's less than 50 minutes away from the thrilling adventures of major theme parks and attractions. Embrace the best of both worlds with tranquility and seamless access to the dynamic attractions of Central Florida. Don’t wait on this gorgeous home, schedule your private showing TODAY!
